com.ihealth.communication.control

Interface Bg5sProfile


  • public interface Bg5sProfile
    Public APIs for the Bg5s serials device profiles

    Clients need to calliHealthDevicesManager.registerClientCallback(com.ihealth.communication.manager.iHealthDevicesCallback) register. When new data from Bg5s device, The CallbackiHealthDevicesCallback.onDeviceNotify(java.lang.String, java.lang.String, java.lang.String, java.lang.String) can be triggered should call.
